OL,6,FMr Adams claims he was subject to a
OL,7,F"grievous smear" while the BBC has
OL,8,Fdescribed the legal action as a
OL,9,F"cynical attempt to launder his
OL,10,Freputation".
OL,12,FThe high-profile republican is seeking
OL,13,Fdamages of at least 200,000 euro
OL,14,F(#168,000) from the BBC.
OL,16,FHowever, the British public service
OL,17,Fbroadcaster has argued it would be a
OL,18,F"cruel joke" to award the former Sinn
OL,19,FFein president any damages.
