OL,6,FOn Thursday, Declan Doyle, SC, for Mr
OL,7,FAdams, said damages awarded to his
OL,8,Fclient should be "very substantial
OL,9,Findeed".
OL,11,FIn his closing statement, Mr Doyle
OL,12,Fsaid the "widespread circulation of a
OL,13,Fnational broadcaster of an allegation
OL,14,Fof a cold-blooded cynical murder"
OL,15,Fcould not be a defamation of anything
OL,16,Fother than "very serious or
OL,17,Fexceptional".
