OL,6,FIn his closing statement, Paul
OL,7,FGallagher SC, representing the BBC,
OL,8,Fsaid the claim made by Martin was
OL,9,Fpresented as an allegation and was
OL,10,Fimmediately followed by Mr Adams'
OL,11,Fdenial, the claim of responsibility by
OL,12,Fthe Real IRA and the state of the
OL,13,FGarda investigation.
OL,15,FMr Gallagher also argued that the
OL,16,Freputation of Mr Adams is important
OL,17,Ffor the case, contending that it was
OL,18,F"universally held" that he had a
OL,19,Freputation of being in the IRA and on
OL,20,Fits Army Council.
