OL,6,FMr Adams denies ever being in the IRA.
OL,8,FOn Friday, Justice Owens outlined the
OL,9,Fkey issues in the case for the jurors.
OL,11,FOn the issue of whether Mr Adams has a
OL,12,Fbad reputation, the judge said the
OL,13,F"onus of proof" was on the BBC to make
OL,14,Fthat case.
OL,16,FHe then referred to the evidence of a
OL,17,Fwitness called by the BBC ` former
OL,18,Fattorney general and Irish government
OL,19,Fminister Michael McDowell.
