OL,6,FEarlier this week, Mr McDowell told
OL,7,Fthe court that Mr Adams was "reputed
OL,8,Fto have become a member of the Army
OL,9,FCouncil of the IRA".
OL,11,FThe judge said Mr McDowell's view and
OL,12,FMr Adams' view on the former Sinn Fein
OL,13,Fleader's role in the peace process are
OL,14,F"poles apart".
