OL,4,Con Irish history'
OL,6,F"But if you come to assess damages in
OL,7,Fthe trial, you're not concerned with
OL,8,Fthat, or to make a historical judgment
OL,9,Fon that, you do what the evidence
OL,10,Ftells you about Mr Adams' public
OL,11,Freputation, about the reputation he
OL,12,Fenjoyed in 2006 and now, in relation
OL,13,Fto those matters," he added.
OL,15,FHe said an historical analysis and
OL,16,Ftheory about the peace process was
OL,17,F"irrelevant".
OL,19,F"No jury, in my view, should be asked
OL,20,Fto give a verdict on Irish history,"
OL,21,Fhe added.
