OL,6,FThe judge later emphasised to the
OL,7,Fjurors they were not being asked to
OL,8,Fadopt the mindset of a journalist or
OL,9,Fjudge when making their decision.
OL,11,F"You're asked, of course, to make the
OL,12,Fdecision, not as journalists, but as
OL,13,Fordinary members of the public, using
OL,14,Fyour common sense," he added.
